{"tid":373990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【渣都冇】澳門大豐銀行通知客戶保險箱水浸　百人焦急排隊查詢","createTime":"2017-08-25T12:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T15:05:22.000Z","uid":36238,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c81557de9753a7d600373f3288e8c8d9874bb988","tid":373990,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>澳門日前遭強颱風「天鴿」襲擊，多處地方水浸，位於低窪地帶的新馬路銀行部份保險箱亦有損失。<br />\n<br />\n近百名市民今日趁銀行重新開門，在新馬路的大豐銀行外排隊等候查看保險箱，有市民擔心可能自己在底層的保險箱已被水浸。<br />\n<br />\n銀行清理積水的人員透露有很大損失，水浸最高達到1.5米，但具體有多少保險箱受損，仍有待銀行點算。</strong><br />\n<br />\n位於澳門新馬路的大豐銀行在颱風停業後，今天首次通知保險箱客戶，表示銀行地庫的保險庫有水浸，不知道客戶的財物是否受損。得知消息後，近百名市民前往大豐銀行，焦急排隊、輪籌，分批進入，清點保險箱物品情況。<strong>澳門大豐銀行由前特首何厚鏵父親何賢等人創立，何厚鏵現時擔任該銀行的名譽董事長。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/200217_7cf6b2dd762e0462d24ac41d6f0116fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F200217_7cf6b2dd762e0462d24ac41d6f0116fa.jpg&h=52c2b8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁小姐是排隊輪候的客戶之一，等待查看放在保險箱裡面的畢業證書、房產證、首飾等貴重物品。她表示有朋友的保險箱放在銀行地庫第四層格，已經查看過，未有浸水。亦有客戶非常擔心，因為自己的保險箱放在最底層，而銀行職員對他說最底層的保險箱被水浸到，第二層則沒事。<br />\n<br />\n記者見到側門有兩名銀行聘請的清理人員，將裡面的積水一桶桶倒出來，桶內的積水有黑色的污泥。一名清理人員向記者表示，<strong>「水浸大概1米多，最多有1.5米。很多損失。」</strong>記者問保險箱是否有事，對方表示有，但是不方便透露具體受損細節。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/200256_9246151106e864261d8d0877b3cd5e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F200256_9246151106e864261d8d0877b3cd5e67.jpg&h=7591f25a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5203b621d2b1d271c32469f8f15ec45503da4c51","tid":373990,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T12:07:07.000Z","msg":"大風銀行"},{"pid":"7a7a6697429c221853c5c733c97ae29c377d0c78","tid":373990,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcb1d7747d3daba783651d8bca700a9faaedeb2","tid":373990,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a793be5d0ca9353c8147bb4b3a39768b29674e4f","tid":373990,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a433806d061d5a139c4b4c81588fad261d5db9fb","tid":373990,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c3e1ee8dcd6c70f119469d086f4fb20ed105c8","tid":373990,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"銀行好似講明保險箱冇得賠?"},{"pid":"6384333948783c02156097fc7673aa7f3a34d8df","tid":373990,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"d泥水倒落坑渠<br />\n會唔會塞渠？"},{"pid":"cb2f3311d63baaf8ff3686ec47f9dae52118fb2b","tid":373990,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d泥水倒落坑渠<br />\n會唔會塞渠？</blockquote><br />\n等封死去水再浸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a08bfa4845933479432b5aa2dfdd57b7761120","tid":373990,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d泥水倒落坑渠<br />\n會唔會塞渠？</blockquote><br />\n等封死去水再浸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解可以咁<br />\n岩岩先浸完<br />\n星期日又有風，係咪又想浸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe035ec79decbfefc9a1cfb60b89411658ab2a5","tid":3739